title: A New and General Biographical Dictionary - 15 Vols
description:
A New and General Biographical Dictionary in 15 Volumes

Containing an Historical and Critical Account of the Lives and Writings of the most 

Eminent Persons in Every Nation; particularly the British and Irish; 

From the Earliest Accounts of Time to the Present Period

Wherein Their Remarkable Actions and Sufferings, their Virtues, Parts, and Learning

are accurately displayed.

With a Catalogue of their Literary Productions.

Published in 1798.
